#~ "may be processed by the queue before the database transaction has "
#~ "committed. When this happens, any updates you have made to models or "
#~ "database records during the database transaction may not yet be reflected "
#~ "in the database. In addition, any models or database records created "
#~ "within the transaction may not exist in the database. If your event "
#~ "depends on these models, unexpected errors can occur when the job that "
#~ "broadcasts the event is processed."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "з•¶е»Јж’ӯдәӢд»¶жҳҜеңЁиіҮж–ҷеә« Transaction е…§еҲҶжҙҫзҡ„жҷӮеҖҷпјҢйҖҷеҖӢдәӢд»¶еҸҜиғҪжңғеңЁиіҮж–ҷеә« "
